    <p>Maps and statistics illustrate each district’s built environment, socio‑economic, and demographic characteristics. Dynamic charts compare conditions across districts.</p>

    <h1>Learn</h1>

    <p>Each community district is unique. Find out about your community board's budget priorities and most pressing concerns, and learn about the projects and neighborhood studies that are happening in your district.</p>

